---

---

<section class="relative bg-[var(--color-surface)] noise-overlay overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Orange radial glow -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[60%] h-full pointer-events-none"
    style="background: radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(255,77,0,0.08) 0%, transparent 60%);"
  ></div>

  <div class="section section-inner relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-[680px]">
      <h2
        class="text-white mb-8 accent-dot reveal"
        style="font-size: clamp(30px, 3.5vw, 44px); font-weight: 700;"
      >
        Every month you wait, the gap gets wider.
      </h2>

      <div class="space-y-6 mb-10 reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.1s;">
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Outdated workflows bleed time. Underused software burns money. Undefined roles create confusion that compounds with every new hire.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          And while your team pushes harder, your margins quietly shrink.
        </p>
        <p class="text-white/70 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          The companies that modernize now will scale. The ones that don't will spend the next five years reacting instead of leading.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal" style="transition-delay: 0.2s;">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
          Book a Free Strategy Call →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
